txt.en: 'A Mead Hall is nothing but a stacked pile of wood unless there are people living near and able to use it. With all the upgrades that have been made, we have a Mead Hall that the Rohirrim would be proud to call their own. If we send out a call, many will answer.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
